{"tid":42892,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去左無印買2017年記事簿 排隊比錢個陣先醒起自己","createTime":"2016-12-17T05:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T15:48:10.000Z","uid":34419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b0e7e6f9b949fb01ae09b4b18c62abd987cb6e","tid":42892,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"今日要返半day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   咁下晝放左工無野做  又因為我未去過無印  就打算去兜個圈  諗住扮下文化人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到個陣  都唔係好覺有幾有文化  好多mk潮童就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我一路行  每次有d mk經過我  都總會同隔離條女講兩句  之後就聽到大聲笑??? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n笑乜春啊  笑笑笑  未見過一條友行街  如果你知我係邊個一定唔夠膽寸我(我心諗  唔敢講)<br />\n<br />\n行行下  見到有本2017年既記事簿  簡約得黎又幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   就拎左本去排隊比錢<br />\n<br />\nwa屌~ 成三十幾人係到排緊隊  咁見都無野做就照排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋本野真係幾靚<br />\n<br />\n排左成十分鐘好似係  重有三個就到我個陣  忽然醒起自己根本無朋友無約會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   買本記事簿記乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩諗到呢到就到我比錢  我又唔敢話唔要  驚個staff以為我玩野  就夾硬比左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本野成$38 而家擺左係到都唔知有乜春用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef55226afab4129aaa32e1b5d0918080f07268d","tid":42892,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"記低每日幾點返工"},{"pid":"713006e821479d55edf9095f2496ae7c7d1cca51","tid":42892,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記低每日幾點返工</blockquote><br />\n一至六都要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得星期日放假 寫低都無用"},{"pid":"61214e87560a7f7b75f6ab365ae8b3f79b84c604","tid":42892,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:27:09.000Z","msg":"mark低d OT數睇下公司出糧有冇出少左"},{"pid":"09dea56d7dc1d1b5444e17697b1c30b7489822fd","tid":42892,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mark低d OT數睇下公司出糧有冇出少左</blockquote><br />\n平時我都有儲開糧單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37c263a0d4c2c44837364a90262cc8611a735ae","tid":42892,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ae737dc7af034dad6e67e8e865d85623951718","tid":42892,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"Mark 底每日洗咗幾多錢"},{"pid":"e765909fdf6bb1a043fbaa4119355b07401a037b","tid":42892,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mark 底每日洗咗幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n返工放工嘅車費 lunch自己帶飯 dinner返屋企食 無朋友唔洗出街"},{"pid":"9760c198b251001372b09991b4a905ba89e68d55","tid":42892,"uid":40170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:39:48.000Z","msg":"洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99411d7f2d6510b050ed943761a2e554612f508d","tid":42892,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"記低每日有幾多cold call，入境處電話"},{"pid":"4455edfb71a98515f70d33f32985f38399a7728e","tid":42892,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"mark低每日俾幾多人恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f916c1a8abc751e715434c228dc8b80d5dd930","tid":42892,"uid":7256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"記得每日發過既夢"},{"pid":"715163b70aa85da8109815fc83ea6a6eea8dcaf8","tid":42892,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得每日發過既夢</blockquote><br />\n每日都係同女神行街 (連拖手都無)"}]}